  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">starship</span>, earned for surveying a host of new worlds during the <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Titan Expedition</span>.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Claim</span> this ship to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current ship. While on a planet, summon ships from the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一艘专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">飞船</span>，这是你在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">泰坦远征</span>期间完成对一系列新世界的测绘行动的奖励。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">领取</span>这艘飞船，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的飞船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在行星上时，使用快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）召唤飞船。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空船</span>，透過<span class=\"name name-stellar\">泰坦探險</span>期間完成諸多新世界調查而獲得。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">領取</span>這艘船加入你的收藏，或是與目前太空船<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 召喚太空船。"
  },
